# ToDo List

A simple ToDo List created using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This application allows users to add, delete, and mark tasks as completed.

## Usage

1. Enter the task text in the input field.
2. Click the "Add" button to add the task to the list.
3. You can mark tasks as completed by clicking on the checkbox next to them. Completed tasks will have text with a strikethrough.
4. To delete a task, click the "Delete" button next to it.

## Local Storage

This ToDo List stores your tasks in the browser's local storage, so they remain available after page reloads.

## Project Development

The project can be improved or extended in the following ways:

- Adding the ability to edit tasks.
- Sorting tasks by different criteria (e.g., date or priority).
- Adding categories or labels to tasks.
- Enhancing the design and styling.

